		   <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform2" ><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=223932"><span id=Scholar>Aarenla</span></a><b><span id=Scholar><br>Scholar</span></b><br><img src=/shared/user_star_ico.gif height=9 width=9><br>86 posts
		   <br><nobr><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [2.77]</nobr><br><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=Aarenla&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform2" width="100%"><p>The way I think of my pally is a &quot;dungeon tank&quot;. I have had the best dungeon experiences on my pally. Make sure about every 3 lvls you max out your casting skills, especially evocation, alteration and abjuration. Those spell lines are your strong suit. Evocation for nuking things (undead especially), alteration to heal yourself during and after battle, and abjuration for buffing and the like. The best places to hunt are dungeons, you can pacify mobs to break up spawns. Also a good thing to look into is a manna pres item or flowing thought later on. Pally is capped at 185 on med until lvl 50 and this can create a bit of downtime later on. Others can probably tell you more but these are the main things I have learned from playing my pally. Good luck and have fun, Pally is a very fun class to play.<br><br><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=780542" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=780542</a><br><br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Wed Aug 27 15:48:50 2003</em></p><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>Of his knowledge a man should never boast,<br>Rather be sparing of speach<br>When to his house a wiser comes:<br>Seldom do those who are silent make mistakes;<br>Mother wit is ever a faithful freind.</td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=right id=fs8 >0 Replies</td></tr></table></td></tr></table><tr><td>
